Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B ,
Happy Thursday!=20
Every week, I record an audio edition of Not Boring. Typically the morning =
of the newsletter, I wake up at 5:30am, head to the basement, record, edit,=
 pick music for, and publish a version of the essay that I read out loud. I=
 have a face for radio and a voice for Twitter, but I like doing the audio =
version because it lets me give you another way to consume these essays tha=
t I spend so much time on.=20
Thing is, while anywhere between 30k - 100k people read each essay (thanks =
for sharing!), about 1,500 max listen to the audio version, despite the rel=
ative ease of consumption. A big part of the reason for the delta? Podcast =
discovery sucks.=20
Today, I=E2=80=99m writing about Podz [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJx=
FkE2OwyAMhU9TllH4S8iCxWzmGogEN0UlQMHpKHP6ocliJMuWbD0_fW-xCGsqh86pIvk0g0cGHe=
GnBkCEQvYKxXin6cAUl2IiTgtHlVTEV3MvAJv1QWPZgeR9Dn6x6FM8FX3PJHloZUfKFbd2Gicx0=
slSLuldqlG6fpzv7PK1u_MQF9DwhnKkCCToB2KuN_51Y9-tgq8IEVNO7rdb0tZWNmfiNesZ7SlT=
7a-UQ0e7RbxBPl8oebqJfltZV_e5ol2eHx0pOiacU_Fxbefnw24QzkMDMG1ue_R4GIh2DuAuNrw=
iOmnNChFKi84Ziy0YSpVgVA6ipXOyNHhOJ6GGiZPm7FJTxX_TP6Myfoc], a company whose =
product I believe has the potential to change that. This is the first time =
I=E2=80=99ve written a sponsored deep dive about a consumer social product =
- all of the rest have been fintech or investing-adjacent - because I assum=
e that if you=E2=80=99re the kind of person who takes the time to read Not =
Boring once or twice a week, you want to learn new things. I think Podz is =
going to make it a lot easier to find new audio content on the subjects you=
 want to learn about, and make it easier for the people who, like me, spend=
 hours behind a microphone recording.=20
Podz only ask out of this is that you try the Podz Beta:
And fill out this survey with your feedback:=20
To encourage you to give feedback, Doug has generously offered to donate $1=
0 to the charity of my choice for every Not Boring reader who fills it out.=
 I chose Alzheimer=E2=80=99s Foundation of America [https://email.mg2.subst=
ack.com/c/eJxFUMtuxCAM_JrlGPFOcuDQS38DQfBm0RJIwdkq_frS7KGSZcsejcYzi0NYSz3NX=
